1. Location Based Market Place
2. Location Based File Sharing
3. Location Based Bulletin Board

Kronologger.com as Location Based Market Place is allow you
to sell and buy your used good things / second hands good thins
like house, car, gadget, home appliance, etc to people around you.

Kronologger.com as Location Based File Sharing is allow you
to share your files to people around you.

Kronologger.com as Location Based Bulletin Board is allow you
to announce news to people around you

